  "body_html": "<div class=\"status\"><span>9:41</span><span>●●● ▢</span></div>\n          <div class=\"top-bar\">\n            <div class=\"tb-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"6\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"18\"/></svg></div>\n            <div class=\"tb-model\">Gemini <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\"/></svg></div>\n            <div class=\"tb-avatar\"></div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"convo\">\n            <div class=\"user-turn\">Explain what a transformer is, simply.</div>\n\n            <div class=\"ai-turn\">\n              <span class=\"ai-spark\"><svg class=\"grad-fill\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 0c.6 5.4 6 10.8 12 12-6 1.2-11.4 6.6-12 12-.6-5.4-6-10.8-12-12C6 10.8 11.4 5.4 12 0z\"/></svg></span>\n              <div class=\"ai-body\">\n                A <strong>transformer</strong> is a neural network architecture that reads an entire sequence at once and learns which parts matter most using a mechanism called <strong>attention</strong>. Instead of processing words one by one, it weighs every word against every other word in parallel — which is why it scales so well to long context.\n                <div class=\"ai-actions\">\n                  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"11\" height=\"11\" rx=\"2\"/><path d=\"M5 15V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h10\"/></svg>\n                  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"23 4 23 10 17 10\"/><path d=\"M20.49 15a9 9 0 1 1-2.12-9.36L23 10\"/></svg>\n                  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"5\" r=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"19\" r=\"3\"/><line x1=\"8.6\" y1=\"13.5\" x2=\"15.4\" y2=\"17.5\"/><line x1=\"15.4\" y1=\"6.5\" x2=\"8.6\" y2=\"10.5\"/></svg>\n                  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"5\" cy=\"12\" r=\"1.6\" fill=\"currentColor\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12